@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 12
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title RAW sockets in stiva (concept)

rectangle "Aplicatie" as APP
rectangle "Transport\n(TCP / UDP)" as L4
rectangle "RAW socket\n(IP / ICMP direct)" as RAW
rectangle "Retea\n(IP)" as L3
rectangle "Acces la retea\n(Ethernet / Wi-Fi)" as L2
rectangle "Mediu fizic" as L1

APP -down-> L4
L4 -down-> L3
L3 -down-> L2
L2 -down-> L1

APP --> RAW : acces direct
RAW --> L3 : ocoleste TCP/UDP

note right of RAW
  Necesita de obicei privilegii ridicate.
  Util pentru diagnostic, cercetare,
  implementari custom.
end note
@enduml